'''Orotoru G'am''' was a [[Podracing/Legends|podracing]] course on the floating [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Orotoru G'am|same name]] on the planet [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]]. It cut through the [[City Plaza (Orotoru G'am)|City Plaza]] all the way to the [[Hall of Heroes (Dac)|Hall of Heroes]].

[[Occo Ninebar]], hailing from the aquatic world of [[Neelabi]], was the track favorite.

